units.shortDescription: Step into luxury and comfort in our stunning 9-bedroom, 5-bathroom villa in Champions Gate. Upon arrival, you'll be greeted by an open living room with plush seating, elegant decor, and abundant natural light, perfect for relaxing after a busy day.
units.longDescription:
The first floor houses two charming bedrooms: one with a cozy full bed, and the other a king master with an ensuite bathroom featuring a large tub and walk-in shower. The kitchen is fully equipped with modern appliances and a large island, spacious dining area. As you ascend the staircase, you'll discover more beautifully designed bedrooms, each equipped for ultimate comfort. Among them, two bedrooms share a Jack and Jill bathroom, each with a queen bed. Another features a serene queen bed, while two more share a Jack and Jill bathroom - one with a queen bed, the other with two twins. Perfect for families with children, the sixth bedroom features a Full/twin bunk bed, and the seventh has three full beds, ideal for larger groups.

Take a dip in the large screened pool and spa or lounge on one of many chairs soaking up the Florida sun. Socialize or read in the lanai area, complete with a seating area and large dining table.

Want to check-in early or have a late checkout? Let us know two days in advance, and for an additional fee, we'll do our best to accommodate your request. pool/ hot tub heating is available for $70 every five days, and if your property has a grill, please note there is a cleaning fee of $50. We provide a washer and dryer for your convenience but kindly ask that you bring your own detergents.

We know that pets are an important part of your family, and we're pleased to offer pet-friendly accommodations for your furry friends. Please note that there is a fee of $250 for damages caused by pets, and we kindly ask that you keep your pets off the furniture during your stay. Restrictions apply please contact our team for further details.

Guest booking must be 21 years of age or older.

we offer our guests access to a variety of amenities at The Oasis Clubhouse. Take a dip in the lazy river, work out at the gym, or challenge your family and friends to a game in the arcade. You can also lounge by the pool and enjoy the Florida sunshine. The Oasis Clubhouse is open from 9 am to 9 pm daily.

Please keep in mind we provide a few toiletries to get you started for your stay, however any additional items would need to be purchased yourself.

This rental property has a Doorbell camera on the exterior of the home pointed toward the street and front door.

node.longDescription:
CHAMPIONS GATE RESORT OASIS CLUB and RETREAT CLUB

Included in your reservation, you will have access to The Oasis Club, an exclusive resort-style club for registered residents of the Champions Gate Community. This beautifully appointed club boasts the lifestyle amenities of some of the finest resorts in the world, right in your own backyard. 

The Oasis Club features:

 Resort Style Pool with Water Slide and Cabanas
 Lazy River & Splash Park
 Tiki Bar
 State -of -the -Art Fitness Center
 Locker Rooms
 Volleyball Courts
 Movie Theatre
 Game Room
 Indoor Restaurant

You also have access to Retreat Club featuring:

 Water slides (40" height requirement single rider)
 Pool
 Splash Pad
 Mini Golf
 Hammocks

Guest access

To access the community, all guests are required to be registered in the resort system. We kindly ask that you provide us with the first and last names of all adult guests at least 48 hours prior to your arrival. This will help expedite your check-in with security, failure to do so may result in delays to your check-in. At the security gate all registered drivers will be required to provide a valid photo ID. 

We offer a starter kit as a courtesy:

 2 Toilet paper per bathroom
 1 Small shampoo per bathroom
 1 Soap per bathroom
 1 Hand soap per bathroom
 2 Trash bags
 1 Dish soap
 1 Sponge
 2 Dishwasher pod
 1 Paper towel

The quantity above is intended to make sure you are comfortable upon your arrival and through the first night of your stay. Please keep in mind that you may need to purchase additional supplies for the remainder of your stay.

TRASH

 Trash pickup is daily
 Have trash out in trash bench by 7am
 Keep trash bench lid closed especially overnight
 All trash must be bagged and tied in 13-gallon kitchen bags and cannot weigh more than 30 lbs.
 Grocery bags are not allowed
 Loose trash will not be picked up.
 No liquids are allowed.
 Boxes need to be folded flat

DELIVERIES

You can receive packages from UPS, Fedex and Amazon. The USPS does not deliver to the home. You are able to receive food deliveries. Driver will show their ID and your order/the property address to guard at gate.

units.longDescription:
On the first floor, you'll find a queen bedroom with an ensuite bathroom and a king master bedroom with a lavish ensuite walk-in shower. 

Upstairs, there are two bedrooms sharing a Jack and Jill bathroom: one with a queen bed and the other with a full bed. Another bedroom offers three full beds, perfect for larger groups. The sixth bedroom is adorned with a playful Minions theme and features a full/twin bunk bed. Two additional rooms are connected by a Jack and Jill bathroom, one with two twin beds and the other with a queen bed. Lastly, there is a queen bedroom for a serene retreat.

Take a dip in the large screened pool/ hot tub or lounge on one of many chairs soaking up the Florida sun. Socialize or read in the lanai area, complete with a seating area and large dining table.
